---
title: Private Read Flow
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant D as Dapp SDK
    participant I as Iframe (PXE)
    participant P as Popup
    participant A as Authenticator

    D->>I: encrypt(keyA, { method: "executeUtility", params })
    I->>P: postMessage({ type: "derive-keys" })
    P->>A: credentials.get() + PRF
    A-->>P: PRF(32B) — biometric required
    P->>P: HKDF(PRF) → protocol keys
    P->>I: postMessage({ protocolKeys })
    I->>I: PXE decrypts notes → computes result → discards keys
    I-->>D: encrypt(keyB, { result })
